HEADWORD: Credulousness
<hw>Cred"u*lous*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Readiness to believe on
slight evidence; credulity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Beyond all credulity is the <qex>credulousness</qex> of
atheists.</q> <rj><qau>S. Clarke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Creed</ent>⟦br⟧
